{
  "texts": [
    "The BRAVO game environment consists of three serious games used by medical and paramedical staff during therapy in combination with a wide range of sensory actuators (e.g.",
    "VR helmet, smart-watch, motion sensors, etc.)",
    "in order to record the active patient behaviour and provide real-time adaptation.",
    "The three categories of serious games implemented in the BRAVO platform are:",
    "-Topological Categories, -Infinite Runner, -Planning."
  ]
}